# File     : GRND020-strong-perm-full-h2-policy.ttl
# Domain   : Deontic Ontology / ODRL Grounding
# Problem  : Strong permission full H2: Disability blocks same assigner prohibition
# Refs     : Mohammed et al., What Does ODRL Mean? FOIS 2026
# Generated: 2026-03-26 by gen_foundation_problems.py
# Links    : Discriminating/GRND020-strong-perm-full-h2-1.p
#            Discriminating/GRND020-strong-perm-full-h2-1.smt2
